const uint8_t *  pLockID,
unsigned  lockIDSize,
uint8_t *  pUnlockKey,
unsigned  maxUnlockKeySize 
)
pure virtual

User supplied method to obtain the unlock-key for the specified radar.

Parameters
pSerialNumberRadar being unlocked
pLockIDStart of memory block containing the devices LockID
lockIDSizeSize of the LockID pointed to by 'pLockID'
pUnlockKeyArea into which the Unlock-Key should be placed
maxUnlockKeySizeMaximum acceptable size of the unlock key (size of 'pUnlockKey' area)
Returns
Size of the Unlock-Key data placed in the 'pUnlockKey' area, or -1 if no key was provided
